{"tid":1464670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不打記者！！不阻求護！！！請廣傳！","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:10:55.000Z","uid":19923,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"25015b4afe8c39464319c299f2688dd2799cd1d1","tid":1464670,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"立場記者都打！仲唔係鬼係咩？<br />\n<br />\n宜家呢個情況我哋最驚就係會有啲狗或者藍絲會扮示威者去做出一啲我哋呢啲示威者根本唔會做嘅嘢，例如冇差別打人，亂咁破壞街上嘅汽車！！如果有一日有啲人想陷害我哋，揸住㗎大貨車衝上街撞路人，咁咪入晒我哋數？醒目啲啦自己人！<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋一定要定立一啲最基本嘅界線唔可以去犯：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係唔可以打記者<br />\n唔可以阻住救護人員做嘢<br />\n不無差別打人<br />\n不胡亂破壞他人財物<br />\n絕對不趁火打劫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果見到有人做呢啲嘢基本上都可以肯定佢係鬼，呢個時候大家應該要合力制服佢哋"},{"pid":"d73411fbaf84c9561be9ba530d6bda35238ed3be","tid":1464670,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:16.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c01dfd4d64394eb6c1847390666db274645b8873","tid":1464670,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f247157155d6ae28dd60a3c8f445d088479cc065","tid":1464670,"uid":62,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"打記者救護點講得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a997e428eadeb5e8f259152f5e55d90ec678d5a5","tid":1464670,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2255581212ef91b2e74a9f248e41575e11883bc","tid":1464670,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.18!!!  NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Z3KL26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Z3KL26.jpg&h=e0e1ab3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qs4BB9M.png\